Product Id: Monthly Retail Trade Survey (Department Store Organizations)
The estimates are based on the 2017 North American Industry Classification System (NAICS).
Quality indicator: Code A=Excellent. Code B=Very good. Code C=Good. Code D=Acceptable. Code E=Poor, use with caution. Code F=Unreliable (data not published).
Retail e-commerce includes e-sales from both store retailers included in NAICS 44-453 and non-store retailers included in electronic shopping and mail order houses (NAICS 45411).
Retail e-commerce sales only include online sales made by Canadian retailers. Purchases made by Canadian consumers from foreign-based retailers are excluded.
